{"tid":775890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇多啦a夢電影會喊？","createTime":"2018-08-11T14:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T17:24:14.000Z","uid":57649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54c3588abf56a41a45c7630b7a3c53604625b5ca","tid":775890,"uid":57649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"最近香港上嗰套金銀島，<br />\n<br />\n我見又川村元氣又星野源咁，所以特登走去戲院睇（平時都係上網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多細蚊仔嘈生哂，但呢套戲出乎意料地好睇。<br />\n<br />\n好睇嘅地方唔係在於佢有幾龐大嘅陣容，幾有張力嘅畫面，幾豪華嘅資源投放，而係有一份純真係套戲到。<br />\n<br />\n可能你地會覺得低b，劇情老套太小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n但正正就係有一份小朋友嘅純真感情喺入面，先至最打動到我嘅心。<br />\n<br />\n每一次同電影版先會出現嘅同伴道別嗰下真係會忍唔住喊出嚟，就算唔喊都會眼濕濕。<br />\n一套多啦a夢電影已經屌打萬千嘅韓劇蝗劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f2779bec953abcb7a9ae330f3c1c48fc107868","tid":775890,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"小夫同胖虎好man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bd566c9001bde0b79931642675520ef2d043b2","tid":775890,"uid":57649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f2779bec953abcb7a9ae330f3c1c48fc107868","tid":775890,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"小夫同胖虎好man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"平時蝦蝦霸霸，反而係最有義氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}